710
00:59:48,986 --> 00:59:51,737
現実超えちゃう未来 アーイ！
A future that transcends reality, aye!

711
00:59:52,237 --> 00:59:55,889
弱点も平気 スイッチでランチャー！
Weaknesses are fine, switch on the launcher!

712
00:59:56,439 --> 01:00:00,153
すなわち特者生存ワンダランDAY 楽しもう！
That is, the privileged survival Wonderland DAY, let's enjoy!

713
01:00:00,465 --> 01:00:01,965
すなわち特者生存ワンダラダー！！ 楽しもう
Which is to say, it's a "Special-Person-Survival Wonderland"!! Let's enjoy it!

714
01:00:02,265 --> 01:00:05,565
面白がれること探したまえ over?
Please look for something interesting, over?

715
01:00:05,965 --> 01:00:08,665
返事聞かせてくれ！
Let me hear your reply!

716
01:00:10,165 --> 01:00:11,865
右左なんかじゃない
It's not about right or left

717
01:00:12,165 --> 01:00:13,865
決めつけて一直線
Decide and go straight ahead

718
01:00:14,165 --> 01:00:16,965
つまり企んだら発射オーライだ！
In other words, if you've got a plan, blast off—all right!

719
01:00:17,165 --> 01:00:19,565
ワクワクさせるぜー！
I'm gonna make it exciting!

720
01:00:27,665 --> 01:00:30,565
みんな、2年目に突入しましたが
Everyone, I've entered my second year, but...

