01:00:30,965 --> 01:00:33,365
まだ楽器の結婚は立ち直っていません！
I still haven't recovered from the "instrument marriage"!

722
01:00:33,565 --> 01:00:36,765
2年目の目標は、ハイ・アップがついたオリジナル曲を出すこと！
My goal for the second year is to release an original song with "High Up"!

