I want to keep a sharp eye out, because I want to be full of spirit

727
01:00:50,165 --> 01:00:53,765
全方位にガッツリ アンテナ張っていなくちゃ！
I've got to keep my antennae fully up in all directions!

728
01:00:54,365 --> 01:00:58,365
いつでも心はちゃんと忠誠でいたいな
I always want my heart to be properly loyal

729
01:00:58,965 --> 01:01:03,565
好奇心は絶えず熱心でいたいなって
I want my curiosity to be constantly enthusiastic

730
01:01:04,165 --> 01:01:08,565
言い聞かせるんだ 調子に乗ったら
I'll tell myself that if I get carried away

731
01:01:08,965 --> 01:01:11,565
すぐ飽きられちゃうから あー！
People will soon get tired of me!

732
01:01:11,965 --> 01:01:15,665
タイトロープもどんとこいでっせ
Bring on the tightrope walk too

733
01:01:16,165 --> 01:01:19,565
すなわち特者生存ワンダラダー！！
Which is to say, it's a "Special-Person-Survival Wonderland"!!

734
01:01:19,965 --> 01:01:21,565
しがみつけ
Hold on tight!

735
01:01:21,965 --> 01:01:26,665
“努力とは最後まで諦めないこと”
“Effort means not giving up until the very end”

736
01:01:26,965 --> 01:01:28,165
メモっておいて！
Take a note of that!

737
01:01:28,565 --> 01:01:32,565
ホントは baby 自信なんかがないよ
To be honest, baby, I have no confidence

738
01:01:32,965 --> 01:01:36,565
ホントは baby 不安ばっかで泣きそうだ
To be honest, baby, I'm full of anxiety and about to cry

739
01:01:36,965 --> 01:01:40,765
でもね baby 挫けないって決めたの
But you see, baby, I've decided not to give up

740
01:01:41,165 --> 01:01:48,665
