So, baby, I want to take on the challenge in uncharted territory, an infinite field!

741
01:01:48,965 --> 01:01:49,965
行くぞ！
Here I go!

742
01:02:00,165 --> 01:02:04,365
前進上等！ ちゃんと歓迎して 高まれ
