743
01:02:04,965 --> 01:02:09,665
海空創造 ちゃんと驚喜して 興奮しよう
Creating sea and sky, let's be properly overjoyed and get excited

744
01:02:10,165 --> 01:02:13,765
僕が言うんだもん 本当にするんだもん
Because I say so, I'm really going to do it

745
01:02:14,165 --> 01:02:17,765
現実超えろ未来 あー！
Surpass reality, the future, ah!

746
01:02:18,165 --> 01:02:20,765
弱点も平気 シンデレラじゃない
I'm fine with weaknesses, I'm no Cinderella

747
01:02:21,165 --> 01:02:24,565
すなわち特者生存ワンダラダー！！
Which is to say, it's a "Special-Person-Survival Wonderland"!!

748
01:02:24,965 --> 01:02:26,765
楽しもう
Let's enjoy it!

749
01:02:27,165 --> 01:02:31,365
面白がれること探し放題でっせ
There are endless interesting things to find

750
01:02:31,965 --> 01:02:35,565
無限のフィールドで
In an infinite field

751
01:02:35,965 --> 01:02:37,565
パニックしなくてもいけ
You don't have to panic

752
01:02:37,965 --> 01:02:39,765
ど真ん中一直線
Go straight through the middle

753
01:02:40,165 --> 01:02:42,665
つまりこれが僕の答えなんだ
In short, this is my answer

754
01:02:43,165 --> 01:02:45,965
胸を張れ！ 今を生きるぞその意味を
Hold your head high! Live in the now, and its meaning

755
01:02:46,365 --> 01:02:49,365
明くる日も明くる日も確かめ進め！
Day after day, confirm it and move forward!

756
01:02:49,665 --> 01:02:50,665
行くぞ！
Here I go!

757
01:03:01,165 --> 01:03:03,665
ありがとー！
Thank you!

